name: Present
description:
Hic et nunc, here and now, aquí y ahora, qui e ora, ici et maintenant.

Does time exist? Past is far away and future we don't know if it will be there. We can only be sure about the present.

Today tomorrow will be yesterday and yesterday's tomorrow is today, we are in the middle where time makes equilibrium.

From the "Reflexiones del Tiempo" series.
One single exposure picture.
